                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[type:fortitude|dc:18|name:Vargouile Venom]</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> Damage the victim has taken from vargouille fangs can't be healed magically.</p>\n<p>Once all vargouille fang damage has been healed nonmagically, the poison ends.</p>"
